  <entry>
    <id>https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/releases/tag/v0.17.0</id>
    <title>New release for Pocket ID: v0.17.0</title>
    <updated>2024-11-26T14:41:48-05:00</updated>
    <author>
      <name>stonith404/pocket-id</name>
    </author>
    <content>&lt;h3&gt;âš  BREAKING CHANGES&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The &lt;code&gt;MAXMIND_LICENSE_KEY&lt;/code&gt; environment variable is now required for IP address lookup in the audit log. In previous versions, this was unnecessary because the GeoLite2 database was bundled with the Docker image. However, continuing to bundle the database would require changing the license of Pocket ID, which is why this change was made.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Features&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;add option to specify the Max Mind license key for the GeoLite2 db (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/commit/fcf08a4d898160426442bd80830f4431988f4313"&gt;fcf08a4&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Bug Fixes&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;don't try to create a new user if the Docker user is not root (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/issues/71"&gt;#71&lt;/a&gt;) (&lt;a href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/commit/0e95e9c56f4c3f84982f508fdb6894ba747952b4"&gt;0e95e9c&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</content>
    <link href="https://github.com/stonith404/pocket-id/releases/tag/v0.17.0" rel="alternate"/>
  </entry>
